{"sn45.171:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 45.171 ","sn45.171:0.2":"14. Oghavagga ","sn45.171:0.3":"Oghasutta ","sn45.171:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn45.171:1.2":"“Cattarome, bhikkhave, ogha. ","sn45.171:1.3":"Katame cattaro? ","sn45.171:1.4":"Kamogho, bhavogho, ditthogho, avijjogho—","sn45.171:1.5":"ime kho, bhikkhave, cattaro ogha. ","sn45.171:1.6":"Imesam kho, bhikkhave, catunnam oghanam abhinnaya parinnaya parikkhayaya pahanaya …pe… ayam ariyo atthangiko maggo bhavetabbo”ti. ","sn45.171:1.7":"(Yatha esana, evam vittharetabbam.) ","sn45.171:1.8":"Pathamam. "}